snippet.title: CORRU.OBSERVER :: LOG 0 :: "So Far" (SPOILERS)
snippet.description:
heads up, this has spoilers for a few moments across all episodes!

things are changing pretty fast, so I wanted to make a little end-of-year video about how far .observer has come, featuring footage from @UElement and a meme from @the_dem.!

P.S., you can listen to the soundtrack for this video here! https://soundcloud.com/corruworks/log-0
